R2_TR3   N_TREF3  0        10k

XU3_1  BAT3_POS  N_SD3    VCC  0  OUT_U3_1  LT1013
XU3_2  N_SC3     BAT3_POS VCC  0  OUT_U3_2  LT1013
XU3_3  N_NTC3    N_TREF3  VCC  0  OUT_U3_3  LT1013

D3_1  N_GP3  OUT_U3_1  1N4148
D3_2  N_GP3  OUT_U3_2  1N4148
D3_3  N_GP3  OUT_U3_3  1N4148
R_PU_GP3  VCC  N_GP3  10k

M_PROT3  BAT3_NEG  N_GP3  0  0  IRFZ44N

*==============================================================
* =================== CELDA 4 - LIBOWER ====================
*==============================================================
R1A_SD4  VCC      N_R1SD4  68k
R1B_SD4  N_R1SD4  N_SD4    2.2k
R2_SD4   N_SD4    0        10k

R1_SC4   VCC      N_SC4    47k
