*==============================================================
.lib C:\Users\jairo\AppData\Local\LTspice\lib\sub\LT1013.sub
.model IRFZ44N NMOS(Level=3 Gamma=0 Delta=0 Eta=0 Theta=0 Kappa=0.2 Vmax=0 Xj=0
+ Tox=100n Uo=600 Phi=0.6 Rs=69.6m Kp=0.25 L=2u W=2.94m Vto=3.7 Rd=0.015
+ Rds=2.4Meg Cbd=1n Pb=0.8 Mj=0.5 Cgso=9.3n Cgdo=0.1n Rg=0.4 Is=81p N=1.09)
